snippet.textDisplay:
Mindmatters101 - Sorry to offend you madam. If I said what I said is upsetting you then I feel that you are allowing yourself to form any opinions whereby you are shutting me up.

Yes you may do the cherry pickings to pick a few from India and a few from Pakistan but I feel that it will be a mish mash. Each of the countries have a distinct way of doing things and mixing them is not a good idea.
